    "description": "<p>\r\n\tARCADIA HOTEL MANAGEMENT PTE. LTD.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\tThe Arcadia Hotel is a stylish modern hotel in the heart of the vibrant Jalan Besar district of Singapore. Located in a former indutrial heritage conservation area, it is a urban retreat with 36 rooms, a rooftop terence with a Jacuzzi, and a cafe. With the hotel conveniently located with amenities close at hand, guest will find the Arcadia Hotel an ideal base for both work and play in Singapore. Inspired by the exciting revitalization of the area. The Arcadia Hotel's rooms provide an abode in the city, offering a peaceful, private and a calm space - creating an ambience of stillness and quiet.</p>\r\n",
